Package om.devservlet.deployment

Interface Summary
QuestionTransporter Used in order to move actual Questions from the Question Developers local machine to the configured locations within the qengine.xml
 

Class Summary
DeploymentRequestHandler Used to handle the actions requested by the Question Developer for the actual deployment of the question(s) to the configured location(s).
QuestionDeploymentRenderer Provides the visual represenation of the different options avaliable for the deployment of the Question(s) selected.
